Woodstock cost $18 for a 3 day pass (in advance), there was no merchandise sold (imagine that!), pot was $15/oz and LSD/mescaline $4 a hit.
The last words spoken or sung at Woodstock - Chip Monck (after Hendrix) with some simple words...""Good wishes, good day and a good life."
